{"tid":160393,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"Robynn & Kendy新歌《無敵》好好聽","createTime":"2017-03-17T16:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T17:16:08.000Z","uid":4260,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6f6b7b96d840133cd121ce1c5f3d224edeec1df","tid":160393,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:17:00.000Z","msg":"Robynn &amp; Kendy - 《無敵》 Law of Love MV <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=siHtQMzofiA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsiHtQMzofiA&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6e4ddca9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=siHtQMzofiA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n甚少聽佢地既歌，但係呢隻歌令我好有驚喜<br />\n張子堅編曲加埋兩女把聲好好聽，成首歌好舒服<br />\n聽埋佢地上一plug既歌，我覺得佢地今年轉路線行得幾好<br />\n暫時係我今年廣東歌top 1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eef4ff88e943a8fbed85b5deac54b7faf568490","tid":160393,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:18:26.000Z","msg":"Robynn &amp; Kendy 其實唱得麻麻<br />\n係studio tune得好姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，編曲就真係ok既"},{"pid":"3c032687a602649df65906147f267d439f68ea83","tid":160393,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:18:53.000Z","msg":"Composed by Robynn Yip/Eric Kwok<br />\nLyrics by 林寶/Robynn Yip<br />\nArranged by Eric Kwok/Robynn &amp; Kendy/張子堅<br />\nPiano by Robynn Yip/Eric Kwok<br />\nElectric Guitar by Kendy Suen<br />\nDrums by Tim Cheng<br />\nAdditional Drum Sound by Eric Kwok<br />\nBass by Chan Siu Kei<br />\nSynth &amp; Midi by Eric Kwok/張子堅<br />\n<br />\n你戴徽章 為立下勝仗<br />\n卻再次遭殃 躺下看月亮<br />\n人空歡喜一場 才明瞭裝不出堅強<br />\n或該一早相信 能爭的 非志向<br />\n<br />\n我再不想 用盡力算帳<br />\n會再次開張 迎來對象到席上<br />\n人生這種沙場 無敵人這麼的誇張<br />\n如相戀出於愛 而失戀 非對向<br />\n<br />\n誰都怕位置 走向後排<br />\n誰可以盡揭 一副好牌<br />\n也許要樂意 拍拍胸懷<br />\n勝利這斷崖 愛亦必須先攀過界<br />\n<br />\n我看見你得獎 未妒忌或敬仰<br />\n再替你鼓掌 原來再未覺異樣<br />\n難得相識一場 同路人怎可不欣賞<br />\n無非都犧牲過 而得失 非對向<br />\n<br />\n誰都怕位置 走向後排<br />\n誰可以盡揭 一副好牌<br />\n也許某日會 明白世界<br />\nIt&rsquo;s just about growing up<br />\nAnd learnin bout how to love<br />\nIt&rsquo;s just about growing up<br />\nAnd learnin bout how to love<br />\n勝利這斷崖 愛亦必須先攀過界<br />\n<br />\n我試過悲傷 道路亦未轉向<br />\n但最後最緊張 尋回往日那月亮<br />\n而人生枉稱沙場 難敵誰初心的馨香<br />\n如果非出於愛 能得的 怎算獎<br />\n<br />\nCos&rsquo; you were just supposed to love<br />\nYou were just supposed to love<br />\nIt&rsquo;s always been enough"},{"pid":"b50741afdffc15fc8d8d15e82b3fd952b5275783","tid":160393,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:22:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Robynn &amp; Kendy 其實唱得麻麻<br />\n係studio tune得好姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，編曲就真係ok既</blockquote><br />\nr&amp;k把聲好夾首歌<br />\n不過我好鍾意張子堅既編曲，好鍾意佢之前編既愛在旁若無人的太空，紙牌屋同心燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2752a9d35ab4dbb7b9cabd42d47f0e4c6e5e20","tid":160393,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f6e8ec546139859de26ee0cfdef082f8a95220","tid":160393,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f38d387447b946a66e2e2fa414ebe33466b6923c","tid":160393,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b71c382fe62cca1b15b7e63fdeaf001196403ad","tid":160393,"uid":90596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s